Ideas for improvement from @gensym:
 - unten baust Du dir einen 'insert_string' zusammen - hier kannst besser
   sprintf oder noch besser https://metacpan.org/module/DBIx::Interp nehmen
 - Getter/Setter mit Moo (https://metacpan.org/module/Moo) vereinfachen

 - handle the following time periods as command line options
   - start date
   - end date
   - previous month
   - current month to date
   - previous year
   - current year to date
 - determine the users and groups for the given period
 - generate the following statistics for the given period
   - number of users
   - available computing power
   - utilised computing power for all users
   - utilised computing power for each user
   - utilised computing power for each group
